main event: A civilian couple observed approximately 12 unidentified objects circling Logan, Utah in formation.
interesting points: The objects were observed for about 1.5 to 2 minutes., They were described as white and possibly tinted., The objects maneuvered in groups of 5., The altitude of the objects was estimated between 2001 to 2200 meters., The sighting took place on September 6, 1967.
